\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 Project overview\

\b0 \
\
Bluerondo.com is a web-based animated visualization of the unique time signature found in Dave Brubeck\'92s 1959 hit \'93Blue Rondo a la Turk\'94. It\'92s meant to bring form to the rhythms found in the song as well as act as a homage to the album\'92s cover art created by talented graphic designer S. Neil Fujita. \

